02:49.637 --> 02:51.405
WALKER: * Lo-o-o-o-ove

02:51.505 --> 02:53.241
What happened
with Treasure's album?

02:55.108 --> 02:56.377
Well, all that work

02:56.477 --> 02:59.747
and Lucious still put out
the original.

03:00.748 --> 03:01.849
(Teri sighs)

03:01.949 --> 03:02.883
You know, every time I try

03:02.983 --> 03:04.418
and do something good
for Empire,

03:04.518 --> 03:05.586
