(cheers and applause)

03:29.377 --> 03:32.045
Welcome back to Tea Talk,
ladies.

03:32.145 --> 03:33.414
How were your weekends?

03:33.514 --> 03:36.384
Well, I, um, got a chance
to catch up

03:36.484 --> 03:38.118
