hold five, six *

09:14.221 --> 09:16.624
(Giselle and Becky screaming)

09:16.724 --> 09:18.759
GISELLE: Girl, oh, my goodness.

09:18.859 --> 09:20.994
Your church performance got
2 million views on YouTube.

09:21.094 --> 09:22.062
What?

09:22.162 --> 09:23.330
Your single, psht...

09:23.430 --> 09:25.398
damn near crashed Spotify.

09:25.498 --> 09:27.400
-So let's raise a glass...
-Yes.

09:27.500 --> 09:31.138
To the first woman to survive
a full-scale cancellation

09:31.238 --> 09:33.306
with her dignity
and her edges intact.

09:33.406 --> 09:35.943
-BECKY: Yes.
-GISELLE: To Tiana, child, yes.

09:36.043 --> 09:38.278
Okay, I'm gonna set down
the soapbox for a while

09:38.378 --> 09:39.947
