measured and thoughtful.

09:56.429 --> 09:57.631
-Absolutely.
-GISELLE: Yes.

09:57.731 --> 09:58.832
We're thinking
of going on tour.

09:58.932 --> 10:00.533
Why don't we shut down
some college campuses?

10:00.634 --> 10:02.602
Tour?
Yes, I love that.

10:02.703 --> 10:03.971
You know what?

10:04.071 --> 10:05.605
Childish Gambino
just gave, like,

10:05.706 --> 10:07.540
custom Jordans
to the first hundred people

10:07.641 --> 10:09.810
that came to his Coachella
performance--genius.

10:09.910 --> 10:12.445
Custom.
Custom like...

10:12.545 --> 10:14.815
-How 'bout Tiana Timbs?
-Boom.

10:14.915 --> 10:16.717
Great,
why don't we mull that over

10:16.817 --> 10:18.018
and then we'll get back to you?

10:18.118 --> 10:19.687
Okay, perfect.
Yay!

10:19.787 --> 10:21.621
-Bossy, Bossy.
-BECKY: Yay, Bossy!

10:23.223 --> 10:25.292
