-(mouthing words)

10:25.392 --> 10:27.527
Oh, shoot.
You know what?

10:27.627 --> 10:28.896
I'm gonna give you guys
my glam squad's info.

10:28.996 --> 10:30.831
I know you haven't
worked together,

10:30.931 --> 10:32.332
but just to let you know,

10:32.432 --> 10:34.968
