on national television

11:44.004 --> 11:47.074
to be humiliated,
those are wins to you?

11:47.174 --> 11:49.209
Okay, where did you get
this degree from, again?

11:49.309 --> 11:50.744
Did you get fired?

11:50.844 --> 11:53.480
-No.
-Did you go off on your cohost?

11:53.580 --> 11:56.884
-No, not this time.
-(laughs)

11:56.984 --> 11:58.919
