12:07.795 --> 12:09.930
-Pretty good.
-DR. WICK: Mm-hmm.

12:10.030 --> 12:11.765
-Well, damn.
-(laughs)

12:11.865 --> 12:13.433
You are growing, Cookie.

12:13.533 --> 12:16.403
I can see the passion
and the light in your eyes

12:16.503 --> 12:18.005
coming back.

12:18.105 --> 12:19.907
So keep going, girl.

12:20.007 --> 12:23.243
Don't let one bad moment
mess up a whole string of good.

12:23.343 --> 12:24.778
(exhales)

12:24.878 --> 12:26.579
Celebrate your victories.

12:26.679 --> 12:28.348
(upbeat hip-hop music playing)

